$\left[\begin{matrix}g_{1}\\g_{2}\\g_{3}\\g_{4}\\g_{5}\\g_{6} \end{matrix} \right] = \left[\begin{matrix} w_{11}^{\rm mid}x_1 + w_{12}^{\rm mid}x_2 + b_{1}^{\rm mid}\\ w_{21}^{\rm mid}x_1 + w_{22}^{\rm mid}x_2 + b_{2}^{\rm mid}\\ w_{31}^{\rm mid}x_1 + w_{32}^{\rm mid}x_2 + b_{3}^{\rm mid}\\ w_{41}^{\rm mid}x_1 + w_{42}^{\rm mid}x_2 + b_{4}^{\rm mid}\\ w_{51}^{\rm mid}x_1 + w_{52}^{\rm mid}x_2 + b_{5}^{\rm mid}\\ w_{61}^{\rm mid}x_1 + w_{62}^{\rm mid}x_2 + b_{6}^{\rm mid} \end{matrix} \right] = \left[\begin{matrix} w_{11}^{\rm mid} & w_{12}^{\rm mid} \\ w_{21}^{\rm mid} & w_{22}^{\rm mid} \\ w_{31}^{\rm mid} & w_{32}^{\rm mid} \\ w_{41}^{\rm mid} & w_{42}^{\rm mid} \\ w_{51}^{\rm mid} & w_{52}^{\rm mid} \\ w_{61}^{\rm mid} & w_{62}^{\rm mid} \end{matrix} \right] \left[\begin{matrix}x_1\\ x_2\end{matrix} \right] + \left[\begin{matrix}b_{1}^{\rm mid}\\b_{2}^{\rm mid}\\b_{3}^{\rm mid}\\b_{4}^{\rm mid}\\b_{5}^{\rm mid}\\b_{6}^{\rm mid} \end{matrix} \right] = {\bf W}^{\rm mid}{\bf x} + {\bf b}^{\rm mid}$

$\left[\begin{matrix}h_{1}\\h_{2} \\h_{3} \\h_{4} \\h_{5} \\h_{6} \end{matrix} \right] = \left[\begin{matrix}{\rm sigmoid}(g_1) \\ {\rm sigmoid}(g_2)\\ {\rm sigmoid}(g_3)\\ {\rm sigmoid}(g_4)\\ {\rm sigmoid}(g_5)\\ {\rm sigmoid}(g_6)\end{matrix} \right]$
$\left[\begin{matrix}z_{1}\\z_{2} \end{matrix} \right] = \left[\begin{matrix} w_{11}h_1 + w_{12}h_2 + w_{13}h_3 + w_{14}h_4 + w_{15}h_5 + w_{16}h_6 + b_{1}\\ w_{21}h_1 + w_{22}h_2 + w_{23}h_3 + w_{24}h_4 + w_{25}h_5 + w_{26}h_6 + b_{2} \end{matrix} \right] = \left[\begin{matrix} w_{11} & w_{12} & w_{13} & w_{14} & w_{15} & w_{16}\\ w_{21} & w_{22} & w_{23} & w_{24} & w_{25} & w_{26} \end{matrix} \right]\left[\begin{matrix}h_1\\h_2\\h_3\\h_4\\h_5\\h_6 \end{matrix} \right] + \left[\begin{matrix}b_{1}\\ b_{2} \end{matrix} \right] = {\bf W}{\bf h} + {\bf b}$
$\left[\begin{matrix}\hat{y}_{1}\\\hat{y}_{2} \end{matrix} \right] = \left[\begin{matrix}{\rm softmax}(z_1) \\ {\rm softmax}(z_2)\end{matrix} \right]$

${\bf W}^{\rm mod}$ $\times$ = $6 \times 2$
${\bf b}^{\rm mod}$ $=6$
${\bf W}$ $\times$ = $2 \times 6$
${\bf b}$ $=2$

def sigmoid(z):
  '''
      
  '''
  return (1+np.exp(-1*z))**(-1)

def softmax(z):
  '''
      
      z: =
      y_hat: =
  '''
  return (np.exp(z) / np.sum(np.exp(z)))

def neural_network(x, w_mid_1, b_mid_1, w_mid_2, b_mid_2, w_mid_3, b_mid_3, w_mid_4, b_mid_4, w_mid_5, b_mid_5, w_mid_6, b_mid_6, W, b):
  '''
      1
      x: 1=D
      w_mid_i: i=D
      b_mid_i: i
      W: =(KxJ)
      b: =K
      D:J:K:
      y_hat: =K
      hi: i
'''
  # 
  # 1
  g1 = np.dot(w_mid_1, x) + b_mid_1
  h1 = sigmoid(g1)
  # 2
  g2 = np.dot(w_mid_2, x) + b_mid_2
  h2 = sigmoid(g2)
  # 3
  g3 = np.dot(w_mid_3, x) + b_mid_3
  h3 = sigmoid(g3)
  # 4
  g4 = np.dot(w_mid_4, x) + b_mid_4
  h4 = sigmoid(g4)
  # 5
  g5 = np.dot(w_mid_5, x) + b_mid_5
  h5 = sigmoid(g5)
  # 6
  g6 = np.dot(w_mid_6, x) + b_mid_6
  h6 = sigmoid(g6)
  


  # 
  z = np.dot(W, np.array([h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6])) + b
  y_hat = softmax(z)

  return y_hat, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6

$\frac{\partial L_{ce}}{\partial {\bf W}_{k}} = (\hat{y}_k - y_k){\bf h}$
$\frac{\partial L_{ce}}{\partial {\bf b}_{k}} = \hat{y}_k - y_k$
$\frac{\partial L_{ce}}{\partial {\bf W}_{j}^{\rm mod}} = \left [ \sum_{k=1}^{K}(\hat{y}_k - y_k)w_{kj} \right ] (1-h_j)h_j{\bf x}$
$\frac{\partial L_{ce}}{\partial {\bf b}_{j}^{\rm mod}} = \left [ \sum_{k=1}^{K}(\hat{y}_k - y_k)w_{kj} \right ] (1-h_j)h_j$

$k$$j$

def cross_entropy(y_hat, y):
  '''
      
      y_hat:  y
      y: 
  '''
  # 10one-hot
  y_onehot = np.zeros(num_classes)
  y_onehot[y] = 1.0

  ce = -1.0 * np.sum(y_onehot*np.log(y_hat))

  return ce

def calc_gradient(y_hat, y, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, W, x):
  '''
      
      y_hat: : =K
      y: : 
      hi: i
      W: =(KxJ)
      x: : =D
      D:J:K:
      grad_w_mid_i: w_mid_i=D
      grad_b_mid_i: b_mid_i
      grad_W: W: =(KxJ)
      grad_b: b: =K
  '''
  # D, J, K
  D = np.size(x)
  J = 6
  K = np.size(y_hat)

  # 10one-hot
  y_onehot = np.zeros(K)
  y_onehot[y] = 1.0

  # 
  grad_W = np.zeros([K, J])
  grad_b = np.zeros(K)
  for k in range(K):
    grad_W[k,:] = (y_hat[k] - y_onehot[k]) * np.array([h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6])
    grad_b[k] = y_hat[k] - y_onehot[k]

  # 
  # 1(W[:,0],h1)
  grad_w_mid_1 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,0])*(1 - h1)*h1 * x
  grad_b_mid_1 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,0])*(1 - h1)*h1
  # 2(W[:,1],h2)
  grad_w_mid_2 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,1])*(1 - h2)*h2 * x
  grad_b_mid_2 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,1])*(1 - h2)*h2
  # 3(W[:,2],h3)
  grad_w_mid_3 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,2])*(1 - h3)*h3 * x
  grad_b_mid_3 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,2])*(1 - h3)*h3
  # 4(W[:,3],h4)
  grad_w_mid_4 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,3])*(1 - h4)*h4 * x
  grad_b_mid_4 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,3])*(1 - h4)*h4
  # 5(W[:,4],h5)
  grad_w_mid_5 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,4])*(1 - h5)*h5 * x
  grad_b_mid_5 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,4])*(1 - h5)*h5
  # 6(W[:,5],h6)
  grad_w_mid_6 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,5])*(1 - h6)*h6 * x
  grad_b_mid_6 = np.sum((y_hat - y_onehot)*W[:,5])*(1 - h6)*h6
  

  return grad_w_mid_1, grad_b_mid_1, grad_w_mid_2, grad_b_mid_2, grad_w_mid_3, grad_b_mid_3, grad_w_mid_4, grad_b_mid_4, grad_w_mid_5, grad_b_mid_5, grad_w_mid_6, grad_b_mid_6, grad_W, grad_b

from matplotlib import animation, rc
from IPython.display import HTML

np.random.seed(0)

# 
lr = 0.2

# 
w_mid_1 = initial_w_mid_1.copy()
b_mid_1 = initial_b_mid_1
w_mid_2 = initial_w_mid_2.copy()
b_mid_2 = initial_b_mid_2
w_mid_3 = initial_w_mid_3.copy()
b_mid_3 = initial_b_mid_3
w_mid_4 = initial_w_mid_4.copy()
b_mid_4 = initial_b_mid_4
w_mid_5 = initial_w_mid_5.copy()
b_mid_5 = initial_b_mid_5
w_mid_6 = initial_w_mid_6.copy()
b_mid_6 = initial_b_mid_6


W = initial_W.copy()
b = initial_b.copy()

# 
color_list = [(0, 0, 1), (1, 0, 0)]
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(7,7))
# 
for k in range(num_classes):
  plt.scatter(X[Y==k,0], X[Y==k,1], color=color_list[k], label='class'+str(k))
images = []

# 
loss_history = np.array([])
# 
acc_history = np.array([])

for epoch in range(60):
  
  # 
  # ()
  shuffle_index = np.random.permutation(np.arange(num_samples))
  X_tmp = X[(shuffle_index)]
  Y_tmp = Y[(shuffle_index)]
  
  loss = 0
  acc = 0
  for n in range(num_samples):
    x = X_tmp[n,:]
    y = Y_tmp[n]
  
    # 
    y_hat, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 = neural_network(x, w_mid_1, b_mid_1, w_mid_2, b_mid_2, w_mid_3, b_mid_3, w_mid_4, b_mid_4, w_mid_5, b_mid_5, w_mid_6, b_mid_6, W, b)
  
    # 
    grad_w_mid_1, grad_b_mid_1, grad_w_mid_2, grad_b_mid_2, grad_w_mid_3, grad_b_mid_3, grad_w_mid_4, grad_b_mid_4, grad_w_mid_5, grad_b_mid_5, grad_w_mid_6, grad_b_mid_6, grad_W, grad_b = calc_gradient(y_hat, y, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, W, x)

    # 2
    if n == 0 and epoch % 2 == 0:
      img = []
      x1 = np.linspace(-3, 3)

      x2 = -1.0 * (b_mid_1 + w_mid_1[0]*x1) / w_mid_1[1]
      img += plt.plot(x1, x2, color='k')
      x2 = -1.0 * (b_mid_2 + w_mid_2[0]*x1) / w_mid_2[1]
      img += plt.plot(x1, x2, color='k')
      x2 = -1.0 * (b_mid_3 + w_mid_3[0]*x1) / w_mid_3[1]
      img += plt.plot(x1, x2, color='k')   
      x2 = -1.0 * (b_mid_4 + w_mid_4[0]*x1) / w_mid_4[1]
      img += plt.plot(x1, x2, color='k')    
      x2 = -1.0 * (b_mid_5 + w_mid_5[0]*x1) / w_mid_5[1]
      img += plt.plot(x1, x2, color='k')
      x2 = -1.0 * (b_mid_6 + w_mid_6[0]*x1) / w_mid_6[1]
      img += plt.plot(x1, x2, color='k')
      

      img.append(plt.text(-2.8, 2.7, 'epoch: '+str(epoch), size='x-large'))
      images.append(img)

    # 
    W -= lr * grad_W
    b -= lr * grad_b
    w_mid_1 -= lr * grad_w_mid_1
    b_mid_1 -= lr * grad_b_mid_1
    w_mid_2 -= lr * grad_w_mid_2
    b_mid_2 -= lr * grad_b_mid_2
    w_mid_3 -= lr * grad_w_mid_3
    b_mid_3 -= lr * grad_b_mid_3
    w_mid_4 -= lr * grad_w_mid_4
    b_mid_4 -= lr * grad_b_mid_4
    w_mid_5 -= lr * grad_w_mid_5
    b_mid_5 -= lr * grad_b_mid_5
    w_mid_6 -= lr * grad_w_mid_6
    b_mid_6 -= lr * grad_b_mid_6
    

    # 
    loss += cross_entropy(y_hat, y)
    # 
    if np.argmax(y_hat) == y:
      acc += 1
  
  loss /= num_samples
  acc /= num_samples
  loss_history = np.append(loss_history, loss)
  acc_history = np.append(acc_history, acc*100)
  print('%d-th epoch: cross entropy = %.3f, accuracy = %.3f%%' % (epoch+1, loss, acc*100))

    label = np.argmax(y_hat)
    # 
    # (-i)
    image[-i, j, :] = color_list[label]
